gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我覺得暑假流流長，做啲自己鍾意做嘅嘢會更加有意義。<br />\n例如我係鍾意畫畫嘅，得閑就多啲畫<br />\n又或者如果你冇乜嘢特別嘅興趣或者專長，就可以用呢一段時間去搵或者培養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a2b4b22a3d1485a780a5c8ab9c4a0455d3d461","tid":306763,"uid":126263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁增值下自己 揾啲野學下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知學咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cfc1b8fc2c62706e8a6e0464b8de53e7bbb5f8","tid":306763,"uid":73002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點到好過要做暑假作業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白卡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHello<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901e9beaed312a5b2c0e383760ac9aa9c556d476","tid":306763,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:24:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁增值下自己 揾啲野學下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知學咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教我"},{"pid":"62a9f7ce43ca6fb7f5640c71b51341288e8b8af7","tid":306763,"uid":126263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有番part time sale person<br />\n上個月癲到除咗星期日之外日日都返工<br />\n但發覺真係好悶，我呢種人係好容易會覺得做重複嘅嘢係好悶好辛苦，辛苦唔係指體力上嘅辛苦，而係精神上嘅辛苦<br />\n所以第時出到嚟社會，我都唔知有咩工係啱我返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我覺得暑假流流長，做啲自己鍾意做嘅嘢會更加有意義。<br />\n例如我係鍾意畫畫嘅，得閑就多啲畫<br />\n又或者如果你冇乜嘢特別嘅興趣或者專長，就可以用呢一段時間去搵或者培養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個真呀，好多野就算你有幾中意都好<br />\n日日係咁重復做都會頂唔順 <br />\n悶到hihi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff222482316ad21bce378d5267d5470e3941437","tid":306763,"uid":126263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁增值下自己 揾啲野學下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知學咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係咁隨便既人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965b0bf090b66f8400dd79d846a402e131af8ff8","tid":306763,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T20:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁增值下自己 揾啲野學下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知學咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係咁隨便既人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n88"}]}